---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About"
  description="Senior Full-Stack Engineer with deep expertise across Vue 3, Cloudflare Workers, GraphQL Federation, and AWS — delivering end-to-end from architecture to production."
>
  <article class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <!-- Page header -->
    <header class="mb-16">
      <p class="text-accent-light text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Engineering as ownership.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        I don't hand off tickets. I own the outcome — from the architecture whiteboard
        to the production deploy, and everything that breaks in between.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-12">
        <!-- Philosophy -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How I work</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Most engineering problems are not technical problems — they're delivery problems.
              The wrong abstraction chosen too early. The integration left for "later". The
              infrastructure decision delegated to someone who doesn't know the business constraints.
            </p>
            <p>
              I solve this by staying in the problem end-to-end. I've designed Cloudflare BFF
              architectures and written the Vue components that consume them. I've modelled
              federated GraphQL schemas and owned the migrations that keep them consistent with
              production data. I've set up the AWS resources and been on call when they misbehave.
            </p>
            <p>
              This is what senior delivery looks like — not "I did my part", but "it's running and I know why".
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Background -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Background</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I've built and shipped production systems across B2B and platform contexts —
              working across the full delivery stack as the person who makes sure the thing
              actually works in production, not just in the demo.
            </p>
            <p>
              My expertise runs deepest at the intersection of frontend architecture (Vue 3,
              TypeScript), edge computing (Cloudflare Workers, BFF patterns), and API design
              (GraphQL, Federation). I'm comfortable in AWS and DevOps territory when the job requires it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Current focus -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Currently</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Exploring AI-assisted engineering — specifically how autonomous agent fleets can
              own the full software delivery cycle. This portfolio was built by one.
            </p>
            <p>
              Open to senior engineering roles and consulting engagements where full-stack
              ownership and delivery speed matter.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar: quick facts -->
      <aside class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted mb-4">Expertise</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            {[
              'Vue 3 + TypeScript',
              'Cloudflare Workers / BFF',
              'GraphQL + Federation',
              'AWS infrastructure',
              'CI/CD pipelines',
              'Data migration',
              'B2B client delivery',
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-light flex-shrink-0"></span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted mb-4">Connect</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <a href="https://github.com/LuisZMarques" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary hover:text-accent-light text-sm transition-colors focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent-light focus-visible:outline-offset-2 rounded">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              github.com/LuisZMarques
            </a>
            <a href="/contact"
               class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary hover:text-accent-light text-sm transition-colors focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent-light focus-visible:outline-offset-2 rounded">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
              Get in touch
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
